## Bowling Analysis

* Total Wickets
* Economy Rate
* Best Bowling Figures
* Top Wicket Takers

## Match Insights

* Toss Impact Analysis
* Venue-wise Results
* Match Outcome Distribution
* Season-wise Trends

## Interactive Features

* Team Filter
* Player Filter
* Season Filter
* Dynamic Visualizations
* Cross-filtering

